Sands Style magazine brims with the glamour, verve, excitement, entertainment and style you would expect to find at The Venetian and The Palazzo Five-Diamond luxury resorts. Each issue features fashion and style, arts and culture, restaurant and cuisine, celebrity and entertainment, shopping, spas, and travel.
